trigger_script
Disk World creator help
trigger_script

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
trigger_script -  This function is called to activate a script in this object.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void trigger_script(string event,
object who,
int override)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^event%^RESET%^ - the name of the event to be triggered,
%^BOLD%^who%^RESET%^ - a reference to the object who triggered the event
%^BOLD%^override%^RESET%^ - the override for the priority

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/inherit/scripting.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function is called to activate a script in this object.
( Can be left blank, best to use file_name( this_player() ) ).
.EP

